Berhenti.

15
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:55,435
Berhenti, tak guna!

16
00:02:06,470 --> 00:02:07,665
Terima kasih.

17
00:02:08,050 --> 00:02:09,955
Terima kasih sebab tumpangkan saya

18
00:02:10,340 --> 00:02:12,285
dan beri nasihat itu.

19
00:02:13,290 --> 00:02:14,524
Tapi terima kasih juga

20
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:17,915
sebab ingatkan saya
yang abang ini psikopat.

21
00:02:39,250 --> 00:02:40,528
[ Sebab inilah mak benci kamu. ]

22
00:02:40,529 --> 00:02:43,999
[ Memperdaya orang dengan senyuman palsu
memang kepakaran kamu. ]

23
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:47,705
Tiada siapa di rumah itu yang rindu
atau mahukan awak di sana.

24
00:02:48,010 --> 00:02:49,505
[ Awak tak ada keluarga. ]

25
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:06,225
Hei, saya ini.

26
00:03:06,700 --> 00:03:08,035
Awak lapang sekarang?

27
00:03:08,900 --> 00:03:10,535
Kita ajak yang lain pergi minum.

28
00:03:11,540 --> 00:03:13,665
Mestilah saya yang belanja.

29
00:03:30,640 --> 00:03:31,925
Biar saya tuangkan.

30
00:03:36,010 --> 00:03:37,775
- Gelas awak penuh?
- Ya.

31
00:03:38,029 --> 00:03:40,669
Berseronok hari ini dan lupakan hari esok!

32
00:03:40,670 --> 00:03:42,215
- Minum!
- Minum!

33
00:03:44,900 --> 00:03:46,299
- Awak mabuk?
- Ya.

34
00:03:46,300 --> 00:03:48,239
- Awak belum mabuk.
- Nah.

35
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,915
- Minum.
- Minum.

36
00:03:53,870 --> 00:03:55,155
Dia dah mabuk teruk.

37
00:03:56,160 --> 00:03:57,479
Dia dah pengsan.

38
00:03:57,480 --> 00:03:58,839
Hei, Jun.

39
00:03:58,840 --> 00:04:01,095
Awak kena bayar semua minuman ini!

40
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:03,515
Dia ajak kita ke sini
dan cakap dia nak belanja.

41
00:04:03,810 --> 00:04:05,315
Dia dah bayarlah.

42
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:06,815
Jun takkan mungkir janji.

43
00:04:08,650 --> 00:04:10,809
Dia membuktikan nilainya sekali lagi.

44
00:04:10,810 --> 00:04:11,819
Sekali lagi.

45
00:04:11,820 --> 00:04:13,709
Awak semua, saya...

46
00:04:13,710 --> 00:04:17,155
Hidup ini pasti mudah saja bagi dia.

47
00:04:17,540 --> 00:04:21,205
Dia kacak, popular dan kaya.

48
00:04:22,070 --> 00:04:24,675
Tiada apa nak dirisaukan, bukan?

49
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:26,615
Dia patut dimarahi
kalau ada yang dia risau.

50
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:29,785
Tapi tak bosankah
kalau hidup tanpa risaukan apa-apa?

51
00:04:31,230 --> 00:04:33,209
Mari kita minum. Minum!

52
00:04:33,210 --> 00:04:35,145
- Minum.
- Minum!

53
00:04:43,500 --> 00:04:45,135
Boleh awak bangun?

54
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:47,075
Ambillah.

55
00:04:47,940 --> 00:04:49,535
Memalukannya.

56
00:04:54,370 --> 00:04:55,565
Kenapa?

57
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:59,125
Tak ada apa-apa.

58
00:04:59,910 --> 00:05:01,669
Tentu saya mengeluh terlalu kuat.

59
00:05:01,670 --> 00:05:03,615
Ya, cukup untuk seluruh bangunan dengar.

60
00:05:04,660 --> 00:05:05,945
Luahkannya.

61
00:05:05,980 --> 00:05:08,495
Awak boleh anggap saya tembok yang cantik

62
00:05:08,710 --> 00:05:10,255
sebab saya takkan cakap apa-apa.

63
00:05:11,790 --> 00:05:14,045
Saya perlu buat banyak kajian

64
00:05:14,520 --> 00:05:17,785
dan profesor itu hanya terima
pembentangan terbaik.

65
00:05:18,260 --> 00:05:21,525
Saya kena periksa soalan dan jawapan.

66
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,855
Jun hanyalah pelajar tahun satu.

67
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:27,685
Jadi saya tak tahu kalau saya
dan Soo-hyun boleh uruskan semuanya.

68
00:05:28,470 --> 00:05:31,245
Macam mana kalau ahli pasukan buat hal?
Awak akan tolong mereka

69
00:05:31,810 --> 00:05:33,095
sebagai ketua kumpulan?

70
00:05:34,850 --> 00:05:37,975
Macam mana dia tahu
mereka akan timbulkan masalah?

71
00:05:42,550 --> 00:05:44,315
[ Soo-hyun ]

72
00:05:47,250 --> 00:05:49,589
- Guna mod getar!
- Kenapa dia telefon lewat malam begini?

73
00:05:49,590 --> 00:05:50,865
Awak tak nak angkat?

74
00:05:54,290 --> 00:05:55,845
Ya, Soo-hyun.

75
00:05:57,770 --> 00:05:59,005
Jun cakap apa?

76
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:04,555
Kenapa?

77
00:06:05,250 --> 00:06:06,845
Saya nak keluar sekejap.

78
00:06:07,050 --> 00:06:08,825
Siapa yang telefon awak pada waktu begini?

79
00:06:09,030 --> 00:06:10,665
Dia berminat dengan awak?

80
00:06:10,970 --> 00:06:12,075
Dia bukan jenis yang begitu.

81
00:06:12,380 --> 00:06:14,585
Jenis lelaki tiada kaitan
dengan dia berminat atau tak.

82
00:06:15,730 --> 00:06:17,945
Kelakuannya agak berbeza.

83
00:06:18,460 --> 00:06:20,935
Dia memang begitu. Jumpa nanti.

84
00:06:22,690 --> 00:06:25,685
Jangan bising.
Siap awak kalau saya terbangun!

85
00:07:06,290 --> 00:07:07,575
Jun?

86
00:07:12,930 --> 00:07:14,475
So-bin, awak rupanya.

87
00:07:15,570 --> 00:07:17,335
Macam mana awak tahu saya ada di sini?

88
00:07:17,460 --> 00:07:19,365
Soo-hyun kata awak ada di sini.

89
00:07:20,500 --> 00:07:22,705
Kamu berdua tentu rapat.

90
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:25,305
Kecuali saya...

91
00:07:25,430 --> 00:07:27,719
Awak tak apa-apa?
Berapa banyak yang awak minum?

92
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:29,435
Tak banyak...

93
00:07:31,590 --> 00:07:33,085
Saya boleh minum lagi.

94
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:36,605
Jom minum lagi...

95
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:43,565
Kenapa? Boleh awak bangun?

96
00:08:00,140 --> 00:08:01,385
So-bin.

97
00:08:02,780 --> 00:08:04,545
Boleh tak awak suka saya?

98
00:08:15,940 --> 00:08:17,305
Kenapa awak tak jawab?

99
00:08:18,890 --> 00:08:20,215
Awak tak suka saya?

100
00:08:24,300 --> 00:08:26,195
Jadi awak pun benci saya juga.

101
00:08:27,510 --> 00:08:30,595
Saya tak benci awak.

102
00:08:31,420 --> 00:08:32,665
Ya, bukan?

103
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:36,275
Saya dah agak awak akan suka saya.

104
00:08:38,550 --> 00:08:40,454
Saya tahu awak akan suka saya.

105
00:08:41,849 --> 00:08:43,225
Sebenarnya

106
00:08:44,839 --> 00:08:47,054
saya suka orang lain.

107
00:08:49,020 --> 00:08:50,215
Apa?

108
00:08:51,050 --> 00:08:53,655
Ada seseorang yang saya suka.

109
00:08:54,740 --> 00:08:55,935
Apa?

110
00:08:57,780 --> 00:09:01,265
Saya tak boleh suka awak
sebab saya sukakan orang lain!

111
00:09:05,130 --> 00:09:07,809
Jun, boleh awak kawal diri awak?

112
00:09:07,810 --> 00:09:09,715
Jun, awak dah tidur?

113
00:09:10,140 --> 00:09:12,525
- Hei.
- Dia dah tidur?

114
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,725
Soo-hyun?

115
00:09:15,420 --> 00:09:16,795
Letak atas saya.

116
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:18,725
Baiklah.

117
00:09:25,500 --> 00:09:26,825
Awak tahu di mana dia tinggal?

118
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:29,425
Apa? Tak tahu.

119
00:09:30,250 --> 00:09:33,465
Tapi saya rasa Hye-ji tahu.

120
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,555
Alamak.

121
00:09:41,030 --> 00:09:42,925
Dia dengar apa saya cakap tak?

122
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:53,750
[ Vila Belia ]

123
00:09:48,420 --> 00:09:49,705
Nampaknya inilah tempatnya.

124
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,705
Alamak.

125
00:10:02,280 --> 00:10:03,689
Tak sangka betul.

126
00:10:03,690 --> 00:10:05,765
Kita dah nak sampai.

127
00:10:14,730 --> 00:10:17,899
Jun, apa kombinasi pintu awak?

128
00:10:17,900 --> 00:10:19,095
Jun?

129
00:10:20,190 --> 00:10:21,515
Saya dah penat.

130
00:10:21,770 --> 00:10:23,145
Tunggu sekejap.

131
00:10:23,580 --> 00:10:25,035
Ini kunci biometri.

132
00:10:26,660 --> 00:10:30,445
Boleh awak membongkok sedikit?

133
00:10:36,160 --> 00:10:37,395
Dekat lagi.

134
00:10:38,400 --> 00:10:40,345
Boleh angkat dia ke atas sedikit?

135
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:43,075
Tak guna.

136
00:10:43,900 --> 00:10:47,785
Tak guna. Tolong berhasil!

137
00:10:49,930 --> 00:10:52,135
Ya! Baiknya dia.

138
00:10:57,940 --> 00:11:00,145
Berjaya! Soo-hyun, cepat masuk.

139
00:11:09,330 --> 00:11:10,965
Awak mesti penat.

140
00:11:14,750 --> 00:11:16,075
Jaket awak.

141
00:11:17,830 --> 00:11:20,255
- Tolong tanggalkan dan saya akan...
- Kenapa awak nak basuh?

142
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:24,085
Betul juga.

143
00:11:25,390 --> 00:11:27,335
Mungkin saya berhak gunakan tandasnya.

144
00:11:29,050 --> 00:11:32,445
Saya pun sama.
Mungkin saya berhak dapat segelas air.

145
00:12:40,980 --> 00:12:42,225
Kenapa?

146
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:44,205
Tak ada apa-apa.

147
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:47,155
- Air dah melimpah.
- Oh, Tuhan!

148
00:12:54,980 --> 00:12:56,475
Awak nak air?

149
00:13:04,040 --> 00:13:06,995
[ Dia dengar apa
yang saya cakap atau tidak? ]

150
00:13:07,560 --> 00:13:08,885
[ Patutkah saya tanya? ]

151
00:13:11,210 --> 00:13:12,495
Terima kasih.

152
00:13:13,010 --> 00:13:15,135
Tunggu sekejap, Soo-hyun.

153
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:20,945
Awak dengar

154
00:13:22,830 --> 00:13:24,105
apa yang saya cakap tadi?

155
00:13:28,280 --> 00:13:30,129
Maksud saya

156
00:13:30,130 --> 00:13:33,739
saya harap awak dengar saya
berterima kasih sebab bawa dia ke sini.

157
00:13:33,740 --> 00:13:36,425
Awak pun penat. Kita patut balik.

158
00:13:38,050 --> 00:13:39,245
Baiklah.

159
00:13:47,330 --> 00:13:49,365
Dia ada masalahkah?

160
00:13:50,900 --> 00:13:52,575
Saya rasa ada sesuatu yang tak kena.

161
00:13:53,580 --> 00:13:54,815
So-bin.

162
00:13:56,130 --> 00:13:57,595
Boleh tak awak suka saya?

163
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:02,915
Dia disukai oleh semua orang. Kenapa saya?

164
00:14:04,230 --> 00:14:05,549
Dia risau tentang sesuatukah?

165
00:14:05,550 --> 00:14:07,185
Awak berfikir lagi.

166
00:14:08,890 --> 00:14:10,525
Tapi awak tak.

167
00:14:11,050 --> 00:14:12,685
Sebab saya tak peduli tentang orang lain.

168
00:14:13,600 --> 00:14:14,755
Tak peduli konon.

169
00:14:15,180 --> 00:14:18,405
Awak suruh saya cari dia
selepas terima panggilan dia.

170
00:14:19,190 --> 00:14:21,429
Kemudian awak datang dan dukung dia balik

171
00:14:21,430 --> 00:14:23,285
ke rumahnya.

172
00:14:23,810 --> 00:14:25,705
Saya panggil itu ambil berat.

173
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:30,325
Saya banyak cakap, bukan?

174
00:14:32,390 --> 00:14:35,035
Saya tak nak jadi
orang terakhir yang dia hubungi,

175
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:36,885
sebab itulah saya telefon awak.

176
00:14:37,930 --> 00:14:39,305
Saya ikut awak ke sana

177
00:14:40,260 --> 00:14:43,135
sebab saya tak nak menyusahkan awak.

178
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:47,795
Ya, kami mungkin bermalam di sana

179
00:14:48,930 --> 00:14:50,525
kalau awak tak datang.

180
00:14:51,090 --> 00:14:52,325
Awak buat dengan baik.

181
00:14:54,340 --> 00:14:56,985
- Dah sampai.
- Selamat malam.

182
00:14:58,520 --> 00:14:59,985
Awak sengaja teman saya balik?

183
00:15:01,560 --> 00:15:04,419
Saya lebih suka awak tak beritahu Jun
yang saya datang.

184
00:15:04,420 --> 00:15:05,649
Kenapa?

185
00:15:05,650 --> 00:15:08,035
Maaf, sikap ingin tahu saya datang lagi.

186
00:15:08,770 --> 00:15:11,335
Awak pasti ada sebab.
Rahsia awak selamat dengan saya.

187
00:15:12,870 --> 00:15:16,215
Saya cuma tak nak dia rapat dengan saya
sebab nak berterima kasih.

188
00:15:17,970 --> 00:15:19,475
Jun memang begitu, bukan?

189
00:15:21,050 --> 00:15:22,775
Kalau begitu selamat malam.

190
00:15:29,850 --> 00:15:32,145
Awak fikir awak kenal dia,
tapi awak tak kenal dia.

191
00:15:33,630 --> 00:15:35,575
Tak guna. Apa-apa sajalah.

192
00:15:37,330 --> 00:15:40,325
[ Vila Belia ]

193
00:16:27,580 --> 00:16:28,855
Ada seseorang

194
00:16:30,130 --> 00:16:31,855
hantar saya balik malam tadi?

195
00:16:39,980 --> 00:16:42,805
Tak guna. Apa yang berlaku?

196
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:03,005
Rambut hitam pendek.

197
00:17:04,230 --> 00:17:05,505
Ini rambut siapa?

198
00:17:09,070 --> 00:17:11,625
- So-bin!
- Hei, Jun.

199
00:17:12,149 --> 00:17:14,665
- Awak tak apa-apa?
- Bagaimana dengan awak?

200
00:17:15,710 --> 00:17:18,315
Saya? Kenapa awak tanya?

201
00:17:19,190 --> 00:17:21,085
Saya tak rasa ia berlaku.

202
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:24,825
Tapi saya ada buat silapkah malam tadi?

203
00:17:26,970 --> 00:17:28,429
Boleh tak awak suka saya?

204
00:17:28,430 --> 00:17:31,464
Saya tak boleh suka awak
sebab saya sukakan orang lain!

205
00:17:35,030 --> 00:17:38,189
Awak ada buat silapkah? Ya.

206
00:17:38,190 --> 00:17:39,875
Bukan kepada saya, tapi...

207
00:17:43,780 --> 00:17:45,155
Maksud saya...

208
00:17:46,160 --> 00:17:49,995
Awak! Macam mana awak boleh
mabuk teruk begitu?

209
00:17:50,420 --> 00:17:53,465
Itu kesilapan awak. Kesilapan besar!

210
00:17:56,630 --> 00:17:58,655
Saya sibuk
dan kena letak telefon sekarang.

211
00:18:03,760 --> 00:18:04,859
Kenapa pula?

212
00:18:04,860 --> 00:18:09,999
[ Panggilan ]

213
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:11,245
[ Semalam, Nam Soo-hyun ]

214
00:18:14,180 --> 00:18:15,645
Saya telefon Nam Soo-hyun.

215
00:18:18,670 --> 00:18:20,615
Saya betul-betul dah buat silap.

216
00:18:29,940 --> 00:18:31,965
Dia tak ingat apa-apa?

217
00:18:32,180 --> 00:18:34,075
Awak bercakap seorang diri lagi.

218
00:18:36,400 --> 00:18:38,999
- Yakah?
- Sesuatu tak diingini boleh berlaku.

219
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:41,645
Awak akan pendamkan perasaan awak
tanpa menyedarinya.

220
00:18:42,430 --> 00:18:43,665
Itu cerita seram.

221
00:18:43,970 --> 00:18:46,005
Apa yang menakutkan ialah muka awak!

222
00:18:46,350 --> 00:18:49,475
- Awak memang nak kena.
- Awak minum semalam?

223
00:18:49,870 --> 00:18:51,009
Tak.

224
00:18:51,010 --> 00:18:54,179
Saya cuma tolong
seorang budak dungu yang mabuk teruk.

225
00:18:54,180 --> 00:18:55,375
Awak buat apa?

226
00:18:55,540 --> 00:18:57,519
Siapa yang berani suruh awak buat begitu?

227
00:18:57,520 --> 00:18:59,115
Kawan bilik awak?

228
00:18:59,770 --> 00:19:01,699
Awak sendiri seorang pembuat masalah.

229
00:19:01,700 --> 00:19:03,809
Saya habiskan usia remaja saya
dengan menjaga awak.

230
00:19:03,810 --> 00:19:05,055
Betul.

231
00:19:05,310 --> 00:19:08,169
Kalau begitu saya akan bayar ganti rugi

232
00:19:08,170 --> 00:19:09,839
atas kesetiaan zaman muda awak.

233
00:19:09,840 --> 00:19:11,695
- Dengan apa?
- Ayam goreng dan bir!

234
00:19:12,350 --> 00:19:14,115
- Makanlah sendiri.
- Baiklah.

235
00:19:15,430 --> 00:19:18,645
- Layan saya sementara saya di sini.
- Saya pasti awak akan terus ada.

236
00:19:19,610 --> 00:19:22,525
- Tiada siapa boleh jamin.
- Awak nak ke mana?

237
00:19:25,730 --> 00:19:27,619
Apa yang lebih menakutkan ialah

238
00:19:27,620 --> 00:19:29,255
persahabatan kita semakin renggang.

239
00:19:30,960 --> 00:19:33,689
Ia takkan pulih
